      "qwen_observation": "The java8_to_java11 step fails with 'ExceptionInInitializerError: com.sun.tools.javac.code.TypeTags' \u2014 a classic symptom of an outdated Lombok annotation processor incompatible with JDK 11+ internal APIs.",
